data.description: Excellent opportunity to own this beautiful 4 bedroom 2.5 bath Amelia Concourse home! Fresh updates inside & out including appliances, exterior & interior paint, new-carpet upstairs, front drive way pavers & landscaping to name a few. This home is in move in condition & ready for its new owners to enjoy! The Amelia Concourse community amenities center offers a clubhouse, pool, kids splash pool, activity pool & playground. One of the standout features of this home is the seamless connection between indoor & outdoor living spaces. Through the doors in the great room, you'll step out onto into a screened Lanai. This space is perfect for dining, barbecues, or simply relaxing & enjoying the gentle Florida breeze. The backyard offers plenty of room for a private pool. Located in the heart of Amelia Concourse, with easy access to top-rated schools, parks, shopping, and dining. Don't miss out—schedule a viewing today & embrace the Fernandina Beach lifestyle!
